@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Closed
Closed --> Processing : update
Processing --> Pending : approve
Processing : entry / log author
Pending --> OnHold : review
OnHold --> Reviewed : process
Reviewed --> Archived : update
Reviewed : entry / log author
Reviewed --> Pending : revert
Archived --> [*]
@enduml